name: THE FAMILY
description:
when I started my first NFT minting, I never imagined where I would get to. day by day I get to know new people who support and inspire me a lot. every edition I made began to meet the collectors. If you receive this work in your wallet, it means that you have already collected my work. whatever the price, whatever the amount, your support is the biggest motivation for me. when you buy my work, then I think you trust my work. so I try not to disappoint you and try to make better works in the future.

you guys are new family to me. I want to say hello to all of you. meet me in the living room. let's talk. Or meet me on twitter account @talecardHEN.

Thanks. May happiness be with us all.
